template <typename T, typename RequiredLP, typename ActualLP>
struct vsip::impl::Adjust_layout
File: ../../../vsip/core/adjust_layout.hpp

Adjust an actual layout policy against a required layout policy.

The resulting layout takes its values from the required layout where it specifies a value, or from the actual layout when the required layout specifies 'Any_type'.
